    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You must be proficient in the weapon used in order to use this technique. You make a Full Attack against the target, gaining an additional attack at your highest attack bonus. All attacks made this round suffer a -2 penalty to the attack roll. Additional attacks do not stack with other non-permanent additional attacks (such as from other techniques).</p>\n\n\n\n",
